'''宫颈炎'''（{{lang-en|Cervicitis}}），是一种女性[[子宫颈|子宫颈]]的炎症。它多因[[性传播疾病|性传播疾病]]感染造成，常见病原体为[[淋病奈瑟双球菌|淋病奈瑟双球菌]]、[[沙眼衣原体|沙眼衣原体]]<ref name="Workowski2006">{{cite journal |author=Workowski KA, Berman SM |title=Sexually transmitted diseases treatment guidelines, 2006 |journal=MMWR Recomm Rep |volume=55 |issue=RR–11 |pages=1–94 |date=August 2006 |pmid=16888612 |doi= |url=http://www.cdc.gov/mmwr/preview/mmwrhtml/rr5511a1.htm |access-date=2014-08-24 |archive-date=2019-08-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190803065818/https://www.cdc.gov/mmwr/preview/mmwrhtml/rr5511a1.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="POC-IT">{{cite web |author=Hynes NA |url=http://hopkins-abxguide.org/diagnosis/gynecologic/cervicitis.html?contentInstanceId=255497 |title=hopkins-abxguide.org |format= |work=Point-of-care Information Technology |publisher=Johns Hopkins University |date=2008-10-30 |accessdate=2010-02-03 |archive-date=2019-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191211054254/http://hopkins-abxguide.org/diagnosis/gynecologic/cervicitis.html?contentInstanceId=255497 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。也可因宫颈手术操作后造成的宫颈损伤，使病原体得以进入损伤部位<ref name=Robbins>{{cite book |author=Mitchell, Richard Sheppard; Kumar, Vinay; Robbins, Stanley L.; Abbas, Abul K.; Fausto, Nelson |title=Robbins basic pathology |publisher=Saunders/Elsevier |year=2007 |edition=8th | pages=716–8 |isbn=1-4160-2973-7 }}</ref>；或对[[杀精剂|杀精剂]]、[[乳胶|乳胶]][[避孕套|避孕套]]的过敏反应引起<ref name="NIH">{{MedlinePlusEncyclopedia|001495|Cervicitis}}</ref>。

== 急性宫颈炎 ==
临床主要为[[白帶_(生理)|白带]]增多，呈黏液脓性，[[阴道分泌物|阴道分泌物]]的刺激可引起[[外阴疼痛|外阴疼痛]]等症状，伴有腰酸、下腹部坠痛及性交出血等症状。它可与[[阴道炎|阴道炎]]、[[子宫内膜炎|子宫内膜炎]]同时发生，也常有下泌尿道症状，如尿急、尿频、尿痛<ref name="Marrazzo2007">{{cite journal |author=Marrazzo JM, Martin DH |title=Management of women with cervicitis |journal=Clin. Infect. Dis. |volume=44 |issue=Suppl 3 |pages=S102–10 |year=2007 |pmid=17342663 |doi=10.1086/511423 }}</ref>。妇科检查中可见到子宫颈充血、水肿、糜烂，有黏液脓性分泌物流出。

== 慢性宫颈炎 ==
慢性宫颈炎多由急性恶化产生，往往是急性宫颈炎治疗不彻底，病原体隐藏于子宫颈黏膜内，形成慢性炎症<ref>{{cite journal|author=卞度宏|title=正确认识和处理慢性宫颈炎|journal=中华妇产科杂志|year=2007|volume=42|issue=1|pages=4-5|url=http://www.cqvip.com/qk/91112x/200701/23843920.html|accessdate=2014-08-24|archive-date=2014-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140826115105/http://www.cqvip.com/qk/91112x/200701/23843920.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。多见于分娩、流产或手术损伤宫颈后，病原体侵入而引起感染。也有情况直接发生慢性宫颈炎者<ref>{{cite journal|author=狄文, 戴岚|title=慢性宫颈炎的最新诊治策略|journal=中国实用妇科与产科杂志|year=2008|volume=1|pages=6-8|url=http://www.cqvip.com/qk/90644a/200801/26293721.html|accessdate=2014-08-24|archive-date=2014-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140826113318/http://www.cqvip.com/qk/90644a/200801/26293721.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。慢性宫颈炎有[[宫颈糜烂|宫颈糜烂]]、[[宫颈息肉|宫颈息肉]]、[[宫颈管内膜炎|宫颈管内膜炎]]、[[宫颈腺囊肿|宫颈腺囊肿]]以及[[宫颈肥大|宫颈肥大]]等几种病理改变形式<ref>{{cite journal|author=郭述真|title=慢性宫颈炎|journal=实用乡村医生杂志|year=2002|volume=2|issue=19|url=http://www.cnki.com.cn/Article/CJFDTotal-FACT200202019.htm|accessdate=2014-08-24|archive-date=2014-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140826114423/http://www.cnki.com.cn/Article/CJFDTotal-FACT200202019.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

